channel.title: Pr0digyScape Beginners first server+client
channel.description:
[center] Well, this is my 317 that i used for my first server and it's getting kinda old so I think I'm going to release it to [/center] [center]the [/center] [center]community for all you people that are just recently starting the RSPS. ;D[/center]
40% I Own Jad for coding.
40% Mike for coding.
12% Me for keeping it alive, hosting, and coding.
8% Pr0digy for being hoster and owner.
(Yes i know they are probably not accuate but atleast i still gave credits.)
Don't Flame me if you don't like it! It's for beginners.
[u][b]PLEASE DON'T LEECH MY WORK![/b][/u]
Features:
-Anti-Syi.
-D Claws (All four hits work. Not Over-Powered).
-Statius.
-Vesta.
-Zuriels.
-Morrigans.
-Dragon Gs.
-Guthix Gs.
-Dual Sgs.
-Slayer Sword.
-Gold Party Hat.
-Skillerz Santa Hat.
-Vibrant Santa Hat.
-Corrupt Robin (Dosen't Degrade!!! It pwns!!).
-All spirit shields.
-God Wars Bosses (Bandos, Sara, and Zammy!).
-Energy Swords Off Halo.
-Gold, Rune, Dragon, Bandos, Barrows Whips.
-All Gs specs.
-BGS, SGS, AGS, ZGS, GGS, DGS, AGS.
-Maiden Blade.
-Ancient Gs.
-Ancient 1h Gs.
-Bandos Scimitar.
-Dragon Kite Sheild.
-Barrows Defender.
-Dragon Plate.
-Full Elite Set (Helm, Legs, And Plate).
-Pk Legend Cape (Has Wings).
-Pkrz Cape.
-All Prayers Work (You can recharge them so you CAN use pray).
-Type ::quests so you dont have to do quests and so you change magics.
-Lava for all water.
-Titan Train (I recomend High levels only) (level 138's).
-Castle War (no waiting outside you goright into the action).
-CorruptSaradomin God and Giant Moles are at Mb (in the back room).
-I like to call this place Suicied, its Crazy Titan and Crazy PikkupStixx (level 6666 ea) ranging is the only way to kill them. (All you get is D-Bones, change it if you want).
-Rune Cbow and Rune Bolts Spec Works, like enchanted bolts.
-Sumoning (no items in stores you can add sorry).
-All Spell Books work fully (I'm pretty sure).
-Kq.
-All emotes work besides Rabit Hop and Scared.
-Runescape eating GFX's (eats one food and the food you click on).
-Veng Other Works just like real RS. Veng Doesn't (change if you want).
-You have to have Verac's on tokill the Kq.
-No items are lost where ever you die, even in pk!
-Pk is at Edgeville, PVP Zone, and Mage Bank.
-Corp. Beast You have to have Spirit Shield with a Sigil attached (and a clan).
-Icey Cavern just to hang out.
-Green Drag Teleport they pile you, careful.
-Jail Teleport just to chill and where the bad people go (located in the crafting guild, in Falador).
-Trees give logs (maple gives Gold Peices).
-Rocks give ores (Brunite gives Gold Peices).
-Crafting is a bit slow and pricey (uncut Onyx is 2m ea).
-Max level is 138 (I have summoning).
-Dragon Scimitar doesn't disappear after you log out.
-And much much more for yourself to see and find out.
What You'll prolly have to do:
-Make a new home. (NUMBER ONE ON YOUR LIST)
-Compile it because I have the Bounty Hunter codes in it and some more cutoms and music, so compile it!
-Make the Dclaws hit higher.
-Make G.E. FTW!
-Edit Shops ALOT!!!
-Make more custom items if you want.
-And more, but you can figure that stuff out.
Now for some pics:
Client Screen: [img]http://i807.photobucket.com/albums/yy356/D4rk3rm4nz/RunescapePrivateservercover.jpg[/img]
D Claws Spec: [img]http://i807.photobucket.com/albums/yy356/D4rk3rm4nz/Amazingdclawspecial.jpg[/img]
Rune C Bow special attack: [img]http://i807.photobucket.com/albums/yy356/D4rk3rm4nz/Runecbowspecialattack.jpg[/img]
Ancient GS one Handed: [img]http://i807.photobucket.com/albums/yy356/D4rk3rm4nz/ancientgsonehanded.jpg[/img]
Ancient GS two Handed: [img]http://i807.photobucket.com/albums/yy356/D4rk3rm4nz/ancientgs.jpg[/img]
Bandos Scimitar: [img]http://i807.photobucket.com/albums/yy356/D4rk3rm4nz/bandosscim.jpg[/img]
Dragon GS (DGS): [img]http://i807.photobucket.com/albums/yy356/D4rk3rm4nz/dgsonthersps.jpg[/img]
Energy Sword From Halo: [img]http://i807.photobucket.com/albums/yy356/D4rk3rm4nz/energyswordfromhaloonmyrsps.jpg[/img]
Saradomin God: [img]http://i807.photobucket.com/albums/yy356/D4rk3rm4nz/saragod.jpg[/img]
D Claws, Corrupt Robin, and Dragon Plate: [img]http://i807.photobucket.com/albums/yy356/D4rk3rm4nz/serverclawsrobinandpl8.jpg[/img]
Just to show Stat, Vesta, Zuriel, and Morrigans: [img]http://i807.photobucket.com/albums/yy356/D4rk3rm4nz/someitems.jpg[/img]
And some other Customs: [img]http://i807.photobucket.com/albums/yy356/D4rk3rm4nz/somemoreitems.jpg[/img]
Starting Screen and Starter Pack: [img]http://i807.photobucket.com/albums/yy356/D4rk3rm4nz/rspsstarterpackandscreen.jpg[/img]
Green Drag Teleport: [img]http://i807.photobucket.com/albums/yy356/D4rk3rm4nz/greendrags.jpg[/img]
Rune Whip: [img]http://i807.photobucket.com/albums/yy356/D4rk3rm4nz/runewhiponmyrsps.jpg[/img]
Gold Whip: [img]http://i807.photobucket.com/albums/yy356/D4rk3rm4nz/goldwhiponmyrsps.jpg[/img]
Dragon Whip: [img]http://i807.photobucket.com/albums/yy356/D4rk3rm4nz/dragonwhiponmyrsps.jpg[/img]
Barrows Whip: [img]http://i807.photobucket.com/albums/yy356/D4rk3rm4nz/barrowswhiponmyrsps.jpg[/img]
Bandos Whip: [img]http://i807.photobucket.com/albums/yy356/D4rk3rm4nz/bandoswhiponmyrsps.jpg[/img]
[size=20pt]I hope you all like my server, tell me if i should put download links in. If you want this to have download links say so in a comment. If you plan to use this for your server or even your client please give me credits. AND DON'T LEECH!!!! [/size]
